{"tid":1587873,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【開始跪了】外電：滙豐斥逾千萬　啟動公關行動挽北京信任","createTime":"2019-09-22T14:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T04:11:00.000Z","uid":104138,"like":38,"dislike":269,"uniUserReply":120,"replies":[{"pid":"969d8c1604d83fbcb3e9a9ca03d39072d34f3c9d","tid":1587873,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"華為副董事長孟晚舟去年在加拿大被捕，滙豐 （00005） 一直被指是告密者，外電最新引述消息指，滙豐已啟動連串針對北京的公關行動，旨在挽回當局對集團的信任。<br />\n<br />\n外電引述滙豐內部文件指，集團將是次的公關行動命名為「北京能見度戰略（Beijing Visibility Strategy）」，表明行動目標是如何在華為問題所引發的挑戰下，保護及提高集團在中國市場的聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐計劃增加250萬美元（折合約1950萬港元）市場推廣開支預算，設計一系列包括社交及傳統媒體、項目贊助及戶外廣告的宣傳，例如增加微信平台的曝光率，以及定期發布微信朋友圈廣告。<br />\n<br />\n報導續指，滙豐中國行長兼行政總裁廖宜建，亦將會到訪內地媒體的編採部門，並會在內地媒體刊發更多廣告。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，由華為事件觸發的風波至今仍未平息，早前滙豐更曾被指有機會列入「不可靠實體清單」。早前另有報導指，滙豐曾向北京當局解釋，當時幫助美國調查華為是「別無選擇」。<br />\n<br />\n隨着集團前行政總裁范寧8月突然下台，甚至有市場揣測與華為事件有關，當時主席杜嘉琪（Mark Tucker）已否認與滙豐傳向美國通報華為可疑交易事件有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2457166/%E3%80%90%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E3%80%91%E5%A4%96%E9%9B%BB%EF%BC%9A%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E6%96%A5%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E3%80%80%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E5%85%AC%E9%97%9C%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%8C%BD%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB?mtc=40001&amp;srkw=%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2457166%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%259A%25B4%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%259B%25BB%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%25BB%2599%25E8%25B1%2590%25E6%2596%25A5%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%258D%2583%25E8%2590%25AC%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2595%259F%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2597%259C%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%258C%25BD%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25BB%25BB%3Fmtc%3D40001%26srkw%3D%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBkn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=980951ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2457166/%E3%80%90%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E3%80%91%E5%A4%96%E9%9B%BB%EF%BC%9A%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E6%96%A5%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E3%80%80%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E5%85%AC%E9%97%9C%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E6%8C%BD%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%BB?mtc=40001&amp;srkw=%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA</a>"},{"pid":"e10aa63be8b81ed7e0716f1e372e5356f5f7d743","tid":1587873,"uid":47605,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"46fd64025c7ace88fb1a2ad9c582165e4697006d","tid":1587873,"uid":104138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726fe55a676ffa2e620b7020b34c42ecbde53c05","tid":1587873,"uid":211461,"like":104,"dislike":2,"score":102,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"屌 咪撚徙錢啦<br />\n好想放撚晒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09a5bbf57fbde9d4466bdcda37596ed29ade1b8","tid":1587873,"uid":23160,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:59:35.000Z","msg":"深喉了"},{"pid":"c9ca9d7d31ca68fc158fe756cfbf0a21333989f0","tid":1587873,"uid":104138,"like":63,"dislike":3,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"726fe55a676ffa2e620b7020b34c42ecbde53c05","tid":1587873,"uid":211461,"like":104,"dislike":2,"score":102,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"屌 咪撚徙錢啦<br />\n好想放撚晒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T14:59:42.000Z","msg":"d 高層真係天真過天真嬌<img src=\"/assets